Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
set_logic_one(25.10)                                      set_logic_one(25.10)

Name
       set_logic_one

Syntax
       set_logic_one

       -help

       <ports_pins>

       Sets ports or pins to logic 1 in the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each set_logic_one parameter. For a  detailed  de-
              scription  of the command and all of its parameters, use the man
              command: man set_logic_one.

       <ports_pins>
              Specifies the list of the ports or pins that are to  be  set  to
              logic 1.

Examples
              * The following command sets the specified port to logic 1:

                set_logic_one [get_ports {din[1]}]

Related Information
              * get_ports

